      "comment": "NANGAR FLY (7) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 3.5 lengths at Gunnedah in a handy 25.06. Draws out wide but has the ability and in winning form. Recorded the quickest time on the card last start. Form reads well for this. GERTIE GOUT (4) turned in a plain effort last time when seventh at Temora over 457m behind Mr. Monarch (27.18) in a Mix. Key player if finds best. TOMMY BLUE (1) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing sixth (30.72) in a Mix at this track. Shapes as one to consider. GRAPEFRUIT YAEKO (5) finished in the placings last start and deserves some thought.",
